data.Name: The Fungineers
data.Description:
9:00pm Doors | 10:00pm Show | 18+ 

Event tickets purchased for shows in The Perplexiplex DO NOT include admission to the Meow Wolf exhibit. If you would like to experience the converged worlds during your visit, exhibit tickets can be purchased separately and are based on availability.

The Fungineers are a alien/puppet band from the land of Once Upona! they came to earth in 2004 to save it from impending boredom! Their out of this world live show is a menagerie  of relatable bangers and deep silly sexy surreal theatricals! their album "EARTH STUFF" is out now!
